'''Mohamed Belhadj Mahmoud''' ({{langx|ar|مُحَمَّد بَلْحَاجّ مَحْمُود}}; born 24 April 2000) is a Tunisian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] for [[Swiss Super League]] club [[FC Lugano|Lugano]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].

==Career==
Mahmoud joined the youth academy of [[Étoile Sportive du Sahel|Étoile du Sahel]] at the age of 7.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mfmsport.ma/%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%b5%d8%a7%d8%b9%d8%af-%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%ad%d8%a7%d8%ac-%d9%85%d8%ad%d9%85%d9%88%d8%af-%d9%8a%d9%88%d8%af%d8%b9-%d8%ac%d9%85%d8%a7%d9%87%d9%8a%d8%b1-%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%86%d8%ac%d9%85-%d8%a7/|title=الصاعد الحاج محمود يودع جماهير النجم الساحلي برسالة مؤثرة - MFM Sport|website=www.mfmsport.ma}}</ref> He made his professional debut with the clb in a 0–0 [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] tie with [[ES Métlaoui|Métlaoui]] on 8 May 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2019/05/08/tunisia/ligue-1/etoile-sportive-de-metlaoui/etoile-sportive-du-sahel/2973702/|title=Métlaoui vs. Etoile du Sahel - 8 May 2019|website=Soccerway}}</ref> On 27 August 2021, he transferred to the Swiss club [[FC Lugano]] signing a four-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sport.ch/fc-lugano/828290/junger-tunesier-verstaerkt-die-bianconeri|title=Live Sport und News|website=sport.ch}}</ref>

